{"type": "article", "id": 14898, "title": "组装书架", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-15T07:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141038xnQVwzEYLFGJKpTd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是意大利设计师 David Dolcini 为 porada 设计的组装式书架，有 40、60、80 厘米三种宽度组合，在木框结构里放置可拆除的玻璃板。下面的单腿支架仿佛把整个书架悬空起来，有空灵的美感。当它单独立在墙边的时候，特质的墙装托架可以帮助支撑，而多个独立书架组装在一起也能当房间的隔断。远看过去所有物品都像悬在木框当中，比一般的书架多了一份轻盈。<a href=\"http://www.daviddolcini.it/index.php?product=50\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142302PEIhZelcS9AgmiMJ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142303bgSemQYNAtuPMF0I.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1112\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.3594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142304JpWmP1oC2iHhunYe.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"617\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75427873\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142305LRijQHepZrO7MPJC.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"993\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.21393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}